ok now that it’s legal legal should i propose? (asking to annoy him)

opening night of life of pi at @americanrep 🎭 proud and lucky to be a co-producer with @ericjkuhn. massive congratulations to playwright @lolita.chakrabarti, director max webster, and the entire design team for a stunning production 🐅 going to broadway in march!!
happy new year from the motherland to all those who experience the passage of time 🌼

baby’s first sundance. thank u @define1497 for creating the first ever south asian lodge and inviting me and so many cool desi folks to park city. and thank u @rishirajani for letting me be your groupie for the weekend 🤘🏽 keep your 👀 on @politesocietymovie @joylandmovie and @avrockwell’s a thousand and one

The Salon was proud to be a community sponsor of @goldhouseco's Toast to Community, Progress, and Opportunity to celebrate all the Asian filmmakers and talent nominated at the Oscars this weekend ✨
⁣
styled by @corylnixon wearing @meals.clothing

thank you thank you thank you to everyone who attended, hosted, organized, embraced tuesday’s special preview of @lifeofpibway to celebrate asian-americans in the arts, sponsored by gold house & the salon 🥹🥰 i’m honored to be a co-producer of this magical show. huge love to the whole company 🐅⁣
⁣
EDIT: there are so many ppl not pictured here who came and helped organize who I love and appreciate dearly (adding this mostly to placate my dad and boyfriend for not including them in this post)⁣
